# Major Workspace Upgrade: Assets, Privacy & Charting

This update transforms the journal into a more complete portfolio management tool for Hiếu. It includes financial privacy, asset growth tracking, and better trade documentation with image uploads.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Data Storage:** Since we are using a local browser environment, images will be stored in **IndexedDB**. 
> - **Limit:** While IndexedDB can store several gigabytes, performance may degrade if you upload hundreds of high-res 4K screenshots. 
> - **Persistence:** These images are stored *only* in this browser. Clearing browser data will remove them.

> [!NOTE]
> **Privacy Mode:** I will implement a "Toggle Eye" icon that blurs all sensitive financial numbers (Total P/L, Total Assets) but leaves the trade pairs visible for review.

## Proposed Changes

### [UI Enhancement]

#### [MODIFY] [index.html](file:///home/digimed/.gemini/antigravity/index.html)
- Add **"Tổng tài sản" (Total Assets)** card to the stats grid.
- Add an **"Eye" icon** next to the header for Privacy Mode.
- Add a **Settings section** to define "Initial Capital" (Vốn ban đầu).
- Add a **Canvas element** for the Equity Curve chart (Biểu đồ tăng tài sản).
- Replace the "Reason" dropdown with a **Textarea**.
- Replace the "Chart URL" input with a **File Upload input**.
- Add a toggle in the form to choose between **% P/L** or **Amount P/L**.

#### [MODIFY] [styles.css](file:///home/digimed/.gemini/antigravity/styles.css)
- Add `.privacy-hidden` class with `filter: blur(8px)` effect.
- Add styles for the chart container.
- Update form layout for better textarea and toggle presentation.

### [Core Logic]

#### [MODIFY] [script.js](file:///home/digimed/.gemini/antigravity/script.js)
- **Asset Calculation:** 
    - `Current Assets = Initial Capital + Sum(Closed P/L)`.
- **Privacy Toggle:** Logic to add/remove the blur class.
- **P/L Conversion:** 
    - If user enters P/L as an *amount*, calculate the % relative to Margin.
    - If user enters P/L as a *%*, calculate the amount.
- **IndexedDB Integration:** 
    - Function to save Blobs (images) to IndexedDB.
    - Function to retrieve and generate ObjectURLs for display.
- **Chart.js Integration:** 
    - Use `Chart.js` to render a line chart of cumulative P/L over time.

